<view class="products">
  <view class="hero">
    <text class="kicker">赛小蜂篮球 Pro</text>
    <text class="title">先免费打起来，再解锁现场能力</text>
    <text class="desc">基础计分永久免费。Pro 用来解锁 MC 音效和球员数据，AI 比分播报因为有语音合成成本，单独按额度使用。</text>
  </view>

  <text class="section-title">Pro 功能</text>
  <view wx:for="{{proFeatures}}" wx:key="id" class="feature-card">
    <view class="feature-head">
      <view>
        <text class="feature-tag">{{item.tag}}</text>
        <text class="feature-name">{{item.name}}</text>
      </view>
      <view class="preview" data-id="{{item.id}}" catchtap="previewFeature">预览</view>
    </view>
    <text class="feature-desc">{{item.desc}}</text>
    <view class="point" wx:for="{{item.points}}" wx:for-item="point" wx:key="*this">{{point}}</view>
  </view>

  <text class="section-title">Pro 获取方式</text>
  <view wx:for="{{proPlans}}" wx:key="id" class="plan-card" data-id="{{item.id}}" bindtap="selectProPlan">
    <view class="plan-main">
      <view class="plan-top">
        <text class="plan-name">{{item.name}}</text>
        <text wx:if="{{item.badge || item.promo}}" class="promo">{{item.badge || item.promo}}</text>
      </view>
      <text class="plan-desc">{{item.desc}}</text>
    </view>
    <view class="price-block">
      <text class="price">{{item.price == '0' ? '免费' : '¥' + item.price}}</text>
      <text class="buy">{{item.action}}</text>
    </view>
  </view>

  <text class="section-title">AI 语音播报包</text>
  <view class="voice-grid">
    <view wx:for="{{voicePlans}}" wx:key="id" class="voice-card" data-id="{{item.id}}" bindtap="selectVoicePlan">
      <text class="voice-name">{{item.name}}</text>
      <text class="voice-price">{{item.price}}</text>
      <text class="voice-desc">{{item.desc}}</text>
      <text class="voice-action">{{item.action}}</text>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="notice">
    <text>首版运营规则</text>
    <text>分享可换 Pro 试用或积分；AI 播报按次数/积分消耗。这样用户能先体验，平台也能控制语音成本。</text>
  </view>
</view>
